arrived this morning?

35
00:02:48.168 --> 00:02:51.706
Yeah. the girlfriend
answered the door. took us
to the kitchen to meet Ethan.

36
00:02:51.839 --> 00:02:55.543
Once we got started.
all the work was in the kitchen
and upstairs bathroom.

37
00:02:55.677 --> 00:02:56.878
so. we never saw 'em again.

38
00:02:57.011 --> 00:02:58.513
Until you found the bodies.

39
00:02:58.646 --> 00:03:00.782
We were finishing up.
I needed a signature.

40
00:03:01.314 --> 00:03:04.018
Called it in.
got my guys outside.
waited for you to show up.

41
00:03:04.152 --> 00:03:05.586
So your crew
was working here all day.

42
00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:07.220
You didn't hear anything.
see anything?

43
00:03:07.354 --> 00:03:08.890
