44
00:03:16.898 --> 00:03:18.866
Ethan Attis was a seeker.

45
00:03:20.668 --> 00:03:22.302
Absorbed in his work.

46
00:03:25.873 --> 00:03:27.909
Saltwater aquarium.

47
00:03:29.077 --> 00:03:30.611
Terrarium.

48
00:03:33.715 --> 00:03:35.116
Get a list of species.

49
00:03:35.717 --> 00:03:39.120
Krista's purse was emptied.
contents scattered.

50
00:03:39.721 --> 00:03:41.421
Could be a botched robbery.

51
00:03:41.956 --> 00:03:45.727
Plastic tubing from
the aquarium corresponds
with ligature marks.

52
00:03:45.860 --> 00:03:47.729
Murder was impulsive.

53
00:03:52.900 --> 00:03:54.202
House was unlocked.

54
00:03:54.702 --> 00:03:57.572
The intruder slipped in.
Ethan caught him. They fought.

55
00:03:57.705 --> 00:03:58.940
Ethan was strangled.

56
00:03:59.073 --> 00:04:02.143
And then Krista came in.
and she was strangled too?

57
00:04:02.275 --> 00:04:03.343
No.

58
00:04:04.244 --> 00:04:07.014
No. she would have screamed.
run. called for help.

59
00:04:07.148 --> 00:04:11.919
Okay. so...
so it was Krista who came in
and surprised the intruder.

60
00:04:12.053 --> 00:04:13.821
and so then
she was strangled first.

61
00:04:13.955 --> 00:04:16.423
That's not it either.

62
00:04:17.725 --> 00:04:19.927
Krista was alone.

63
00:04:20.494 --> 00:04:22.163
Krista was alone.

64
00:04:22.295 --> 00:04:24.732
The intruder
came in on her...

65
00:04:37.078 --> 00:04:39.213
I see the car
every day at the same time.

66
00:04:39.346 --> 00:04:41.516
Thank you.
Hey. Will. Wait up. Will.

67
00:04:42.917 --> 00:04:46.486
The neighbor said that Attis
had the same housekeeper
every day for years.

68
00:04:46.621 --> 00:04:48.222
Today's the one day
she's not here.

69
00:04:49.056 --> 00:04:52.059
