- Yeah. I'll track her down.

70
00:04:57.598 --> 00:04:59.133
I know.

71
00:05:00.168 --> 00:05:02.236
I could barely get out
of bed this morning.

72
00:05:07.074 --> 00:05:08.509
Weird scene. huh?

73
00:05:10.077 --> 00:05:11.612
What's your take on it?

74
00:05:11.746 --> 00:05:13.614
Honestly. I. uh...

75
00:05:15.583 --> 00:05:17.518
I have no idea
what happened in there.

76
00:05:54.155 --> 00:05:55.189
Hey.

77
00:05:55.323 --> 00:05:57.325
Hey. how's it going
with the plumbers?

78
00:05:57.457 --> 00:05:59.527
Well. so far background checks
are all clean.

79
00:05:59.660 --> 00:06:02.163
We're cross-checking statements
for any inconsistencies.

80
00:06:02.296 --> 00:06:04.832
Looks like Ethan Attis was
some kind of smarty-pants. huh?

81
00:06:04.966 --> 00:06:07.235
Former professor.
research centered on longevity.

82
00:06:07.367 --> 00:06:12.173
He left academia to work for
this startup biotech thing.
BeneFuturum.

83
00:06:12.306 --> 00:06:13.841
"Death is optional"?

84
00:06:13.975 --> 00:06:15.209
Yeah.

85
00:06:15.343 --> 00:06:16.878
You've been pregnant
for three years.

86
00:06:17.011 --> 00:06:18.746
Thirty-eight-and-a-half weeks.
thank you very much.

87
00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:21.414
Perfectly normal human
gestation period.

88
00:06:21.549 --> 00:06:23.416
I can't remember a time
when you weren't pregnant.

89
00:06:23.551 --> 00:06:26.254
I'm sorry. is my pregnancy
hard on you two?

90
00:06:26.386 --> 00:06:28.356
I'm just waiting for a toddler
to walk out of your baby oven.

91
00:06:28.488 --> 00:06:31.192
All right.
Ethan was fired a year ago.

92
00:06:31.325 --> 00:06:34.629
The official story is that
the CEO. Ward Falcon--

93
00:06:34.762 --> 00:06:36.564
That is not his name. I refuse.

94
00:06:36.697 --> 00:06:41.202
Falcon said that. uh.
Ethan's research was
"insufficiently monetizable."

95
00:06:41.335 --> 00:06:44.538
They were seen last month
at a public event
exchanging words.

96
00:06:44.672 --> 00:06:46.073
Witnesses said it got heated.

97
00:06:46.207 --> 00:06:48.242
Okay. Well. we should
go talk to Ward Falcon.

98
00:06:48.376 --> 00:06:49.310
Okay.

99
00:06:49.442 --> 00:06:50.578
Hey.

100
00:06:51.245 --> 00:06:52.680
