-You find something?

128
00:08:14.161 --> 00:08:16.797
I don't know. Um. not sure yet.

129
00:08:17.798 --> 00:08:21.769
So. um. my mom
is packing up Amanda's house.

130
00:08:21.902 --> 00:08:24.338
