131
00:08:24.472 --> 00:08:26.307
I can have them
sent to your place.

132
00:08:26.941 --> 00:08:28.476
No. um. that's...

133
00:08:31.779 --> 00:08:32.713
Can you. uh...

134
00:08:32.847 --> 00:08:34.315
