135
00:08:35.950 --> 00:08:37.051
Thank you.

136
00:08:38.319 --> 00:08:40.021
Sorry you had to--

137
00:08:40.154 --> 00:08:41.322
It's fine. It's fine.

138
00:08:41.455 --> 00:08:43.657
Um. I've got the victim's
housekeeper coming in.

139
00:08:43.791 --> 00:08:45.526
