00:09:36.545 --> 00:09:38.746
<i>And then Krista came in.</i>
<i>and she was strangled too?</i>

147
00:09:38.879 --> 00:09:42.083
<i>No. she would have screamed.</i>
<i>run. called for help.</i>

148
00:09:42.216 --> 00:09:47.121
<i>Okay. so...</i>
<i>so it was Krista who came in</i>
<i>and surprised the intruder.</i>

