<i>That's not it either.</i>

151
00:09:52.460 --> 00:09:54.829
<i>Krista was alone.</i>
<i>Krista was alone.</i>

152
00:09:57.264 --> 00:09:59.733
<i>The intruder</i>
<i>came in on her...</i>

153
00:10:30.865 --> 00:10:32.933
Faith. I think
someone just tried to...

