that disagrees.

197
00:13:40.588 --> 00:13:41.989
Wilbur Trent.

198
00:13:42.590 --> 00:13:43.857
have a seat.

199
00:13:47.428 --> 00:13:48.362
I have been taking care

200
00:13:48.495 --> 00:13:49.463
