gonna tramp in more mud?

206
00:14:04.445 --> 00:14:07.515
Ethan's lady friend.
Krista Sanderton.
what can you tell us about her?

207
00:14:07.649 --> 00:14:10.518
- I don't know.
-  She's a-a receptionist somewhere.

208
00:14:11.619 --> 00:14:12.754
