214
00:14:27.334 --> 00:14:28.902
And you and Ethan never...

215
00:14:29.036 --> 00:14:31.138
No. no. No.

216
00:14:31.606 --> 00:14:33.073
No. of course not.

217
00:14:33.207 --> 00:14:35.409
