221
00:14:45.152 --> 00:14:48.889
Ms. Hughes.
did Ethan ever mention
his old boss. Ward Falcon?

222
00:14:49.022 --> 00:14:50.391
Definitely not.

223
00:14:50.991 --> 00:14:54.562
He hasn't mentioned
his name since the day
he left the company.

224
00:14:54.696 --> 00:14:57.097
No. Ethan hated him.

225
00:15:01.335 --> 00:15:03.705
Detectives.
this is Mr. Falcon.

226
00:15:04.238 --> 00:15:06.440
If you're looking for a chair.
you won't find one.

227
00:15:07.074 --> 00:15:08.543
Movement is medicine.

228
00:15:08.676 --> 00:15:10.779
You're welcome to use
a walking pad
during our meeting.

229
00:15:10.911 --> 00:15:12.112
I'm good. Thanks.

230
00:15:12.246 --> 00:15:14.816
Sure. I could use
a few extra miles today.

231
00:15:14.948 --> 00:15:16.049
Jackie.

232
00:15:16.751 --> 00:15:18.185
How can I help you. gentlemen?

233
00:15:18.318 --> 00:15:21.155
We wanted to discuss
your former employee.
Ethan Attis.

234
00:15:21.288 --> 00:15:24.057
Oh. yeah. I was so sad
to hear that he died.

235
00:15:24.191 --> 00:15:27.261
